text: Guebwiller is a commune in the Haut-Rhin department in Grand Est of eastern France. It is northwest of Mulhouse at the foot of the Vosges mountains. The town had a population of about 11,609 people as of 2006. ==Twin towns== Guebwiller is twinned with: * Lucerne, Switzerland * Castelfiorentino, Italy ==Other websites== * Official Website Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin Category:Subprefectures in France
